<a href="http://eq.crgaming.com/archives.asp?Day=19&Month=1&Year=2000&ID=675&Action=View" target="_blank">http://eq.crgaming.com/archives.asp?Day=19&Month=1&Year=2000&ID=675&Action=View</a>
