Quote:
<br />

<br />
GZ confirmed that the soft cap on Charisma is 200
<br />

<br />
For those unfamiliar with how a soft cap works, once a stat goes over 200 the actual real benefit diminishes. In practical terms this means an increase of a stat from 190 to 200 gives greater benefit than increasing it from 200 to 210.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
